{"tid":1744414,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(J09選區)雙順 老人村加popo集中營","createTime":"2019-11-21T17:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T17:55:19.000Z","uid":300475,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"96374c3d3014b77258a9caf97f2601d5b0bf9570","tid":1744414,"uid":300475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:04:56.000Z","msg":"首先 呢個區選民人口有3分1都係順利紀律部隊宿舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要 加埋40幾年樓齡 第一代居屋屋苑裡面既廢老們 乜都唔知唔去投票 又或者俾人洗腦 真係好驚守唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三個候選人 2藍1黃<br />\n其中一個前警長 唔洗講佢咩色啦<br />\n另外一個係而家現任 行到邊都見到佢個撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好驚守唔住呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位雙順手足 一定要捉哂屋企啲廢老去投票呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">希望popo家屬會厭遠唔去投</span>"},{"pid":"e26b9ec3aa2cf79cfeda4fa2c99784adfa64356c","tid":1744414,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:05:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f383c56f5d7aa869fabf2ac11417c43bd8580513","tid":1744414,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2799df981e0ccdc75a